[SPEAKER_01] Duh ljubavi.

242
00:18:52,339 --> 00:18:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da se nesevično daruju za nas.

243
00:18:56,920 --> 00:19:02,240
[SPEAKER_01] A da mi budemo što bolji.

244
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:06,859
[SPEAKER_01] Blagoslovi mene.

245
