[SPEAKER_01] Brata i sestru.

247
00:19:13,079 --> 00:19:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] I se one koji se brinu o mene.

248
00:19:19,819 --> 00:19:21,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pomoci mi Isuse.

249
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pomoci mi Isuse.

250
