253
00:19:27,299 --> 00:19:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

254
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] Je li bilo teško?

255
00:19:29,619 --> 00:19:30,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

256
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:33,259
[SPEAKER_01] E ovako možete svaki dan.

257
00:19:33,259 --> 00:19:35,740
[SPEAKER_01] Reci.

258
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ššššššššššššššššššššššššššššššš.

259
00:19:39,460 --> 00:19:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kako da se reki mi molimo za brata i sestru kad nemamo brata?

260
00:19:45,420 --> 00:19:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] A jesi, jesi pitao mamu i tatu?

261
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Možda ćeš imat?

262
00:19:48,619 --> 00:19:52,640
